request.description:
### Create Default Rule

This endpoint allows the creation of a default rule for mentoring.

#### Request Body

- `type` (string): The type of the rule.
- `target_field` (string): The target field for the rule.
- `is_target_from_sessions_mentor` (boolean): Indicates if the target is from sessions mentor.
- `requester_field` (string): The requester field for the rule.
- `field_configs` (null): Field configurations (if any).
- `matching_operator` (string): The matching operator for the rule.
- `requester_roles` (array of strings): The roles of the requester.
- `role_config.exclude` (boolean): Indicates if the role should be excluded.


#### Response

The response is in JSON format with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "responseCode": {"type": "string"},
    "message": {"type": "string"},
    "result": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "created_at": {"type": "string"},
        "updated_at": {"type": "string"},
        "id": {"type": "integer"},
        "type": {"type": "string"},
        "target_field": {"type": "string"},
        "is_target_from_sessions_mentor": {"type": "boolean"},
        "requester_field": {"type": "string"},
        "field_configs": {"type": "null"},
        "matching_operator": {"type": "string"},
        "requester_roles": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {"type": "string"}
        },
        "role_config": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "exclude": {"type": "boolean"}
          }
        },
        "created_by": {"type": "integer"},
        "updated_by": {"type": "integer"},
        "organization_id": {"type": "integer"},
        "deleted_at": {"type": ["string", "null"]}
      }
    },
    "meta": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "formsVersion": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id": {"type": "integer"},
              "type": {"type": "string"},
              "version": {"type": "integer"}
            }
          }
        },
        "correlation": {"type": "string"},
        "meetingPlatform": {"type": "string"}
      }
    }
  }
}

